### Register Reader
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "helloguys",
  "email": "hello@example.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "fullName": "hello guys",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "RIDDHI@example.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Change role to AUTHOR
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users/1/role?actorUserId=99
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "AUTHOR"
}

### Suspend user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users/1/status?active=false&actorUserId=99

### Search users by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/search?username=reader

### View audit logs (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Platform analytics (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin/platform-analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### OAuth Google login start (browser flow)
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth2/authorization/google

### OAuth GitHub login start (browser flow)
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth2/authorization/github
